    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total stunner! This car is in truly flawless condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells just like it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this ride since day one, so you won't find a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere. It drives like an absolute dream! I know I'm still building up my rating here, so I\u2019d love for you to come by, take a look, and see for yourself just how perfect this car is. You\u2019re going to fall in love!",
