    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Offering a pristine 1993 Mazda RX-7 FD, a true masterclass in front-midship engineering. This example features the legendary 13B-REW power plant with sequential twin-turbocharging, delivering linear boost across the rev range. The chassis maintains its factory 50:50 weight distribution, paired with an untouched double-wishbone suspension for surgical turn-in. Mechanically flawless, the rotary housing shows exceptional compression across all faces, and the 5-speed manual transmission engages with crisp, short-throw precision. Zero vacuum leaks, original paint with deep luster, and a cockpit devoid of typical bolster wear. A definitive collector-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
